title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: The Vinewood Club Garage Vehicle Workshop Expansion
content:
The Vinewood Club Garage’s Vehicle Workshop makes it easier than ever to access various new modifications, including HSW Upgrades, Imani Tech, and colored headlights. To add Drift Upgrades, visit the LS Car Meet at least once. To add Benny’s Supermod Upgrades, drop by Benny’s Mod Shop.

You’ll need a GTA+ Membership to use The Vinewood Club Garage and all its features and perks.
